      "role": "user",
      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start with the brand names, but I want to dig deeper into the actual *look*. When people talk about \"urban\" style in a more specific way—like when people mention the \"inner city\" look or the vibe in certain neighborhoods—what kind of specific clothing profiles or \"types\" of people/subcultures are usually being referenced? Like, how would you describe the typical look of someone from a heavily urban, minority community compared to a more suburban streetwear look?",
